    <h5>Basic Usage</h5>

    <ol>
        <li>
            <strong>View Weekly Menu:</strong>
            <ul>
                <li>Access the system and navigate to the weekly menu section.</li>
            </ul>
        </li>

        <li>
            <strong>Create a New Menu:</strong>
            <ul>
                <li>Choose to create a new menu from the list of available foods, sorted by student preference scores.</li>
            </ul>
        </li>

        <li>
            <strong>Review and Record the Menu:</strong>
            <ul>
                <li>Review the selected menu and record the chosen items.</li>
            </ul>
        </li>

        <li>
